<svg width="100%" viewBox="0 0 684.94 480" role="img" style="" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
  <title style="fill:rgb(0, 0, 0);stroke:none;color:rgb(255, 255, 255);stroke-width:1px;stroke-linecap:butt;stroke-linejoin:miter;opacity:1;font-family:&quot;Anthropic Sans&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, sans-serif;font-size:16px;font-weight:400;text-anchor:start;dominant-baseline:auto">Email assistant architecture diagram</title>
  <desc style="fill:rgb(0, 0, 0);stroke:none;color:rgb(255, 255, 255);stroke-width:1px;stroke-linecap:butt;stroke-linejoin:miter;opacity:1;font-family:&quot;Anthropic Sans&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, sans-serif;font-size:16px;font-weight:400;text-anchor:start;dominant-baseline:auto">A flowchart showing an email assistant pipeline: inbox to triage to LLM agent with tools, and four memory types feeding in from the right.</desc>
